<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>로그인 - SmartPantry</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #f2f2f7;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --primary-text: #1c1c1e;
            --secondary-text: #8e8e93;
            --accent-blue: #007aff;
            --border-color: #e5e5e5;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            color: var(--primary-text);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* 배경에 은은한 그라데이션 추가 */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.8) 0%, rgba(242,242,247,0) 70%);
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .login-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 380px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .login-card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 50px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo-area {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
            animation: bobble 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .app-name {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--primary-text);
        }

        .app-subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--secondary-text);
            margin: 5px 0 0;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .input-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-text);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }

        .input-field {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 15px;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .input-field:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent-blue);
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(0,122,255,0.1);
        }

        .input-field::placeholder {
            color: #c7c7cc;
        }

        .login-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 18px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: var(--accent-blue);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.1s ease;
            margin-top: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,122,255,0.2);
        }

        .login-btn:hover {
            background-color: #0063cc;
        }

        .login-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        .helper-text {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--secondary-text);
        }

        .helper-text a {
            color: var(--accent-blue);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* 애니메이션 정의 */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes bobble {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }

        /* 모바일 대응 */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .login-card {
                padding: 40px 20px;
                border-radius: 25px;
            }
            .logo-icon {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
            }
            .app-name {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-card">
            <div class="logo-area">
                <div class="logo-icon">📦</div>
                <h1 class="app-name">SmartPantry</h1>
                <p class="app-subtitle">내 손안의 스마트한 저장고 관리</p>
            </div>

            <form action="/login" method="POST">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="id">아이디</label>
                    <input type="text" id="id" name="id" class="input-field" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요" required autocomplete="username">
                </div>

                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="pw">비밀번호</label>
                    <input type="password" id="pw" name="pw" class="input-field" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요" required autocomplete="current-password">
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="login-btn">로그인</button>
            </form>

            <div class="helper-text">
                 <p>아직 계정이 없으신가요? <a href="/register">회원가입 하기</a></p>
            </div>
            <a href="/auth/kakao" style="text-decoration: none;">
                <div style="background-color: #FEE500; color: #000000; padding: 15px; border-radius: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <span style="margin-right: 10px;">🟡</span> 카카오 로그인
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/auth/google" style="text-decoration: none;">
                <div style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #000000; padding: 15px; border-radius: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;">
                    <span style="margin-right: 10px;">⚪️</span> 구글 로그인
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>